# Notes:
# For Gmail:
# 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication in your Google Account
# 2. Go to myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. Select Mail and Windows Computer
# 4. Copy the generated password and paste it in EMAIL_PASSWORD